Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.61,0:01:09.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内定者面談、やっぱり間に合わなかったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:10.44,Eden,Saki,0,0,0,,Looks like I won't make it in time for the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:19.12,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,The missile downed a plane, too.
